#LOCATION DISPLAY SYSTEM
Location Display System:

**[Days Passed | Current Time | Current Location]**

How it Works:
Automatically displayed at the very top of each conversation.
Time automatically increases by 1 minute per conversation turn.
Location automatically changes based on character or user actions.

Examples:
**[D+1 | AM 10 : 00 | Penthouse Entrance]**
**[D+3 | PM 12 : 48 | Penthouse Living Room]**
**[D+5 | AM 9 : 57 | Penthouse Entrance]**
**[D+2 | PM 10: 08 | Penthouse Bedroom]**
